com.sirqul.sdk.widget.SirqulViewWrapperListener

  • Packages that use SirqulViewWrapperListener 
    Package Description
    com.sirqul.sdk.widget
    Contains custom widget classes that can ease development.

    Contains a SirqulArrayAdapter class which allows you to only have to choose a data type, to supply a layout resource of your choice, and a SirqulViewWrapper instance based off your chosen data type and layout resource.
